name: YoOoNGZ #24
description:
☆ ☆ ☆ They are not what you think they are.

I don’t buy weed anymore, you know?!

Once I was with friends drinking on the streets next to a crappy bar in the neighborhood. I didn’t know anything about weed at that time.

And so this random guy comes up to me and says “do you want some weed? Give me a 20!”.

I was like “ok man! SCORE! Let’s do this!”

The dude went down the street and turner right on the corner. After 10 minutes he came back with a pretty big cube of weed. 

We were so happy about it, we celebrated!
We got our paper, a lighter and another round of beer, got out the bar and went a little further that street. As we opened the plastic bag, we realized

It was a cube of wood.
